{"tid":509891,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"欣宜宣布今晚個閪膽有人幫手止痕","createTime":"2017-12-25T21:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:46:32.000Z","uid":151774,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"154459a949fa48c44f03f3628c6bfc43b8761245","tid":509891,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:00:39.000Z","msg":"【冧爆扮鹿】 晒合照公佈戀情？欣宜面貼面賀聖誕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嚟到聖誕佳節，通常喺各大社交平台都會上映「閃光彈攻防戰」，一對對情侶走晒出嚟大晒恩愛亂放閃光彈，一個人過「剩誕」嘅真係唔小心啲都會被閃盲，而欣宜喺呢個聖誕節都喺IG貼出同一名男子嘅親密合照，仲寫道：「Reunited on Christmas with the love of my life!」（於聖誕節與我生命中的最愛重逢），想襯聖誕節公開戀情。我地嘗試打電話俾欣宜了解下，點知一通左電話就聽到有把男聲話唔好阻住佢屌閪，似乎欣宜今晚有著落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/045446_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F045446_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9b2b425e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31eeaf257af57553288a30b0b9e8bdb2af7d9898","tid":509891,"uid":91156,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:08:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22a11cdcaf6eea3b960367fbe5c719aedee9df51","tid":509891,"uid":151774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"31eeaf257af57553288a30b0b9e8bdb2af7d9898","tid":509891,"uid":91156,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:08:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:12:16.000Z","msg":"希望佢地白頭到老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d929588d156cbaf52611077c4c6090328a464b","tid":509891,"uid":44243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:13:30.000Z","msg":"唔好阻住欣宜強姦佢"},{"pid":"e91cab7cb2f90f204dc61f77c7fbde4168b0b5b3","tid":509891,"uid":31914,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:26:09.000Z","msg":"張相成個頭浪係個男人膊頭度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個膊頭會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\"