0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BczKRE6lEb0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBczKRE6lEb0%2F&d=ZHGxvMuO0tRv%2B7Y2z5pkRYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=69b5adc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBczKRE6lEb0%2F&h=69f939fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/BczKRE6lEb0/</a>"},{"pid":"e122c140c5d541d7789d099c28425914781f388c","tid":509891,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"<em>點知一通左電話就聽到有把男聲話唔好阻住佢屌閪</em><br />\n<br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6141dda02d4da06010c265646f2e909b4a679f9e","tid":509891,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"欣宜早前在社交平台貼上一張男友人的照片，但她否認拍拖：「我哋識咗好耐，我叫佢老公，佢叫我老婆，好熟嘅，其實佢係我第一個男友，但同佢唔會有機會，因為佢𠵱家鍾意男人。」"},{"pid":"6d2b69abca80ea75846ad99e91e9f5ec4cdb6e23","tid":509891,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】鄭欣宜昨現身銅鑼灣舉行《一點粉紅》快閃活動 ，鼓勵市民支持同志社群。欣宜表明自己愛男仔，不會改變性取向，但也接納身邊的同志朋友，又自爆17歲認識的初戀男友是男同志，目前保持友好關係。她說﹕「初戀男友一開始已表明是雙性戀者，我當時覺得沒什麼，一齊玩、拖手仔，覺得可以接受他。」她期待前度11月來港，順道邀請對方欣賞自己演出。有機會再續前緣嗎？她笑說﹕「唔會啦，我比不上他那些男友。」"},{"pid":"f37a228fcb81b0816b7723dfd4ddd01573896022","tid":509891,"uid":18456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:59:25.000Z","msg":"嘩 你真識食"},{"pid":"01fe6e59994a501f32887e03d8b65578eb472ef4","tid":509891,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"鄭欣宜前日在Instagram上載與男生手拖手合照，留言以「My sweet husband（我的甜心老公）」稱呼對方，鄭欣宜今日出席活動時解釋，對方是她的初戀男友，自小已經用「老公老婆」互相稱呼，不過對方已公開表示喜歡男生，所以二人不會復合。<br />\n<br />\n鄭欣宜又強調與同公司的關心妍沒有不和，毋須把事情看得很嚴重。"},{"pid":"a280e27fdbc14327a925ce17366b4850f6361086","tid":509891,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T03:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/110830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F110830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=78a91823&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68ad8b12a894a63b2432413497cddd8cf18ee75b","tid":509891,"uid":112197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"比欣宜搞到轉機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}